@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jfkput(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.cos(((v1 + 0.55 / v1 + 0.67) - (v1 + 0.42 + tmp + 0.77)))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.abs(v1))
    v0 = wp.sin(0.72)
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.sin(tmp + 0.09)) + v2)
    data[tid] = v0
